Package: VisKEGG
Type: Package
Title: Plotting functions for MOVIDA project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Edoardo", "Filippi",
      email = "edoardo.filippi@uni-mainz.de",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A package providing functions to generate interactive graphs from KEGG pathways.
    you can use it to visualize pathways, map de results onto pathways, and explore relationships between genes, proteins, and compounds.
    There are functions to convert between different ID types (e.g., UniProt to KEGG).
